OL,3,CThe killers in Wales jailed for life
OL,4,Cin 2025
OL,6,FOver a dozen people across Wales have
OL,7,Fbeen jailed for life this year for
OL,8,Fkilling another person.
OL,10,FThis year we have seen brutal cases in
OL,11,FWelsh courts ranging from a man who
OL,12,Fwas jailed after continuing to punch
OL,13,Fan unconscious individual, a "barbaric
OL,14,Fand cruel" stabbing and grandparents
OL,15,Fwho were found guilty of murdering
OL,16,Ftheir defenceless grandson.
OL,18,FWhile some defendants admitted murder,
OL,19,Fsome initially pleaded guilty to
OL,20,Fmanslaughter but were found guilty of
OL,21,Fmurder by a jury at a trial.
