OL,6,FHere is a rundown of the killers who
OL,7,Fhave been jailed for life by judges in
OL,8,FWelsh courts in 2025:
OL,10,FChristopher Cooper
OL,12,FChristopher Cooper was jailed for life
OL,13,Fafter he killed a "timid, fun-loving
OL,14,Fman" with a single punch from behind
OL,15,Foutside a pub in Swansea.
OL,17,FCooper, 39, punched Kelvin Evans once
OL,18,Fto the head outside The Station Hotel,
OL,19,FGorseinon on May 26 2024 after feeling
OL,20,F"slighted" over his partner's karaoke
OL,21,Fsinging.
