OL,6,FJoseph Dix, 26, and Macauley Ruddock,
OL,7,F28 were sentenced to life imprisonment
OL,8,Fat Swansea Crown Court after
OL,9,Fcontinuing to punch an unconscious man.
OL,11,FThe two men were staying in the
OL,12,FTravelodge on Princess Way, having
OL,13,Ftravelled to Swansea for work.
OL,15,FOn 16 July 2024 they went drinking in
OL,16,Fthe city centre and met 33-year-old
OL,17,FAndrew Main and his friend, who were
OL,18,Falso staying in the Travelodge.
