OL,6,FIn the early hours of 17 July 2024
OL,7,Fwhen they had all returned to the
OL,8,FTravelodge, a disagreement took place
OL,9,Fand a fight broke out.
OL,11,FMr Main was chased by Dix and Ruddock.
OL,12,FDix punched him to the head from
OL,13,Fbehind, knocking him unconscious.
OL,15,FDix and Ruddock continued to punch him
OL,16,Fto the head and face as he lay
OL,17,Funconscious on the pavement.
