OL,6,FMr Main was taken to hospital but
OL,7,Fnever regained consciousness and died
OL,8,Fjust under a month later on 14 August
OL,9,F2024 from his injuries.
OL,11,FThe defendants had pleaded not guilty
OL,12,Fto murder, but were convicted after a
OL,13,Ftrial.
OL,15,FOn 24 January 2025, Dix was sentenced
OL,16,Fto life imprisonment and ordered to
OL,17,Fserve a minimum of 13 years and 176
OL,18,Fdays.
