OL,3,CThe killers in Wales jailed for life
OL,4,Cin 2025
OL,6,FJoanna Wronska was jailed for life for
OL,7,Fthe murder of her partner Marcin
OL,8,FKoziol.
OL,10,FWronska killed Marcin with a single
OL,11,Fstab wound to the heart.
OL,13,FShe claimed he had inflicted the
OL,14,Finjuries on himself in a bid to take
OL,15,Fhis own life.
OL,17,FBut a jury saw through her lies and
OL,18,Fconvicted her of murder after less
OL,19,Fthan 90 minutes of deliberations
OL,20,Ffollowing a nine-day trial at Mold
OL,21,FCrown Court.
