OL,6,FShortly before 6.15pm on 23 October
OL,7,F2023, police received a call from
OL,8,FWronska, who told officers Marcin had
OL,9,Fa knife.
OL,11,FOfficers arrived at their home and
OL,12,Fwere directed to Marcin who was lying
OL,13,Fin bed with a large stab wound to his
OL,14,Fchest. No knife was found in the room
OL,15,Fbut one matching the wound was later
OL,16,Ffound in the kitchen sink.
