OL,6,FPaul Rosser 50, from Gendros, was
OL,7,Ffound guilty of the murder of 27-year-
OL,8,Fold Joshua Norman by a jury following
OL,9,Fa trial at Swansea Crown Court.
OL,11,FThe court heard how, on September 11,
OL,12,F2024, at 12:08pm, officers were called
OL,13,Fto Cwm Road in Hafod to reports of a
OL,14,Fstabbing.
OL,16,FOfficers attended, alongside
OL,17,Fparamedics, and Joshua Norman was
OL,18,Ffound with a significant injury to his
OL,19,Fneck. Despite the best efforts of
OL,20,Fthose at the scene, he was pronounced
OL,21,Fdead shortly after.
