OL,6,FMatthew Battenbough was sentenced to
OL,7,Flife imprisonment for the murder of a
OL,8,Fwoman in her own home.
OL,10,FBattenbough, 34, will serve a minimum
OL,11,Fof 20 years and 10 months in jail
OL,12,Fafter bludgeoning Leanne Williams to
OL,13,Fdeath with a frying pan, scissors and
OL,14,Fknife in Swansea.
OL,16,FMs Williams was found dead at her flat
OL,17,Fin the Townhill area in February,
OL,18,Fhaving suffered extensive injuries
OL,19,Fincluding blunt and sharp force
OL,20,Finjuries to her face and neck.
